		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">David Perry – Executive Video Game Industry Consultant is a 24-year video game industry veteran, Perry launched his professional career at just 15 years of age by writing video game programming books in his native Northern Ireland.  Since then, Perry/Shiny has developed numerous games (including The Terminator, Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles, Mc Donald’s Global Gladiators, 7-Up’s Cool Spot, Disney’s Aladdin, Earthworm Jim, MDK, Sacrifice etc.) his most recent games have sold over 6 million copies based on the Matrix franchise.  Perry sits on the Advisory Board of the Game Developers Conference, and is a regular speaker at key industry events like E3.</span></td>
